data.description: "LUXURY FEATURES" This condo features 2 bedroom, 2 baths, a living and dining room and a balcony. Every condo features a washer and dryer, large walkin closets, track lighting, beautifully designed exterior structures, vaulted celings and breakfast bars in every condo. "COMMUNITY HIGHLIGHTS" Community amenities include cabana with BBQ, Lounge Bar, indoor racquetball court, billiard room, & a fitness center. With nearby access to the Saw grass Expressway, this community is close to the Sawgrass Mall and Bank Atlantic Center, as well as shopping, dining and the entertainment of Ft. Lauderdale and Miami.
